  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/413ec2772edcf35d1ee42791cb398f85.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>In order to escape the dungeon, the girl unseals the demon. This action is wrong and fatal, she does not get the demon's gratitude, on the contrary, the girl is in extreme danger. Will the poor girl be able to outrun the demon and escape this horrible place alive?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/33ab781cb822199fe525227d9e2a3450.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 /></span><br>It is a side-scrolling action game. The characteristic of this game is that you need to run as fast as possible. Because if you are too slow, the monster will catch up with you and eat you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/377d372ed9d0854a754ecb1e363b1781.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/377d372ed9d0854a754ecb1e363b1781.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/377d372ed9d0854a754ecb1e363b1781.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Failure doesn't get you down, and you're confident that you'll find a way to cope with it the next time. You will truly feel strong.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/27347756772a5066190f71cfc2b13d99.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/27347756772a5066190f71cfc2b13d99.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/27347756772a5066190f71cfc2b13d99.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a side-scrolling action game, the character will have common abilities such as rolling, continuous jumping, climbing walls, etc. Our protagonist will have none of them missing. And at the beginning of the game, you will have all the abilities, and you won't leave any regrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game includes 2 difficulties and 140 levels. There are countless mechanisms and secret paths. Each level is carefully crafted and tested. It won't be too difficult to make you feel helpless, nor too easy to make you bored.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>All in all, I'd say it's a good piece of game. I hope it brings you joy.",
