atic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/27347756772a5066190f71cfc2b13d99.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/27347756772a5066190f71cfc2b13d99.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a side-scrolling action game, the character will have common abilities such as rolling, continuous jumping, climbing walls, etc. Our protagonist will have none of them missing. And at the beginning of the game, you will have all the abilities, and you won't leave any regrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/dc3c854d4d66fe69f141aae6a8fa5127.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game includes 2 difficulties and 140 levels. There are countless mechanisms and secret paths. Each level is carefully crafted and tested. It won't be too difficult to make you feel helpless, nor too easy to make you bored.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.poster.avif?t=1709971077\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.webm?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600580/extras/c69f3c8c4a6a224e3cc683c89f3ab5c3.mp4?t=1709971077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>All in all, I'd say it's a good piece of game. I hope it brings you joy.",
